@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vfoxtw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.96 * v0 + 0.98) / wp.exp(tmp + 0.27)) / wp.abs((v1 + 0.90 - v2 + 0.88)))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.exp((tmp + 0.08 + v0 + 0.45)))
    tmp = v0
    tmp = wp.abs((0.95 + wp.cos(v2 + 0.83)))
    v0 = (0.76 / v1)
    v2 = (v2 - (tmp * 0.09))
    data[tid] = v0
